SECTION 1. Tennessee Code Annotated, Title 69, Chapter 9, Part 5, is amended by
adding the following as a new section:
It is unlawful for any person to own, operate, or to allow another person to
operate a personal watercraft upon the waters of Tennessee unless such person is able
to furnish proof of financial responsibility for the operation of the personal watercraft in
the amounts specified in ยง 55-12-102(12)(D)(i).
SECTION 2. This act takes effect July 1, 2025, the public welfare requiring it.
